@startuml
participant AppShellComponent
participant NotificationStreamService
participant NotificationService
participant NotificationBellComponent
participant SnackBarService

AppShellComponent -> NotificationStreamService : start SSE
NotificationStreamService -> NotificationService : GET /notifications/stream
NotificationService --> NotificationStreamService : notification event
NotificationStreamService --> NotificationBellComponent : update unread count
NotificationStreamService --> SnackBarService : emit toast if visible
@enduml
